message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with signal processing and audio analysis. cs.CL is also likely as it deals with natural language processing and speech recognition, which can be applied to bird calls. cs.LG is another possibility as it deals with machine learning and neural networks. cs.CV is also possible as it deals with computer vision and image/sound recognition. cs.AI is less likely but still possible as it deals with artificial intelligence and machine learning.
